===早年===
艾瑪·莫拉諾是家裏8個孩子（5女3男）中的長女<ref name="lastampa1">{{it icon}} [http://www.lastampa.it/2011/11/29/italia/cronache/i-miei-anni-di-storia-d-italia-purnE6hXLpLBAUv5TPxsiN/pagina.html "I miei 112 anni di storia d'Italia"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lastampa.it/2011/11/29/italia/cronache/i-miei-anni-di-storia-d-italia-purnE6hXLpLBAUv5TPxsiN/pagina.html |date=20161202204309 }}</ref>。她的家庭可謂長壽之家：母親和伯母的壽命都高於90歲，一個妹妹安吉拉·莫拉諾（Angela Morano，1908–2011）死於102歲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.verbaniamilleventi.org/angiolina-sono-102 |title="ANGIOLINA", SONO 102! |publisher=Verbaniamilleventi.org |date=2007-03-27 |accessdate=2013-05-05 |language=it |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106034030/http://www.verbaniamilleventi.org/angiolina-sono-102/ |archivedate=2013-11-06 }}</ref>。為了方便父親找工作，艾瑪·莫拉諾一家只好搬家<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.caffe.ch/ws/video/?video_id=637 |title=La nonna che abbraccia tre secoli |publisher=Caffe.ch |date=2010-11-12 |accessdate=2013-05-05 |language=it |archive-date=2016-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331154937/http://caffe.ch/ws/video/?video_id=637 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於[[氣候|氣候]]不佳，當地的一個醫師建議他們住一些氣候較好的地方。於是他們遷到了近[[馬焦雷湖|馬焦雷湖]]的[[韋爾巴尼亞|韋爾巴尼亞]]。1926年，艾瑪嫁給了喬凡尼·馬丁路齊（1901–1978）<ref name="Emma113">{{cite web|author=mario.giovanardi|url=http://www.vip.it/emma-marano-113-anni-mangio-tre-uova-al-giorno-come-mi-disse-il-dottore-quando-ero-ragazza|title=Emma MArano 113 anni Mangio tre uova al giorno, come mi disse il dottore quando ero ragazza|publisher=Vip.it|accessdate=2013-05-05|language=it|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015011008/http://www.vip.it/emma-marano-113-anni-mangio-tre-uova-al-giorno-come-mi-disse-il-dottore-quando-ero-ragazza/|archivedate=2013-10-15}}</ref>，1937年，他們生育了1個孩子，但6個月後孩子早夭<ref>"Emma Morano, 112 anni: ha visto dieci Papi. Il segreto? Tre uova al dì" (in Italian). 45.9215067,8.5515597: Blitzquotidiano.it. Retrieved 2013-05-05.</ref>。他們的婚姻並不美滿，在翌年就[[分居|分居]]，喬凡尼也被逐出家門。然而這段婚姻關係卻一直維持到1978年喬凡尼去世。

===晚年===
她之後在一間[[黃麻|黃麻]]工廠工作直到1954年，隨後她在聖瑪麗亞書院（一間[[寄宿學校|寄宿學校]]）的廚房工作，工作到75歲退休<ref>(Italian) "I miei 112 anni di storia d'Italia"</ref>。她直到115歲生日時仍然獨居<ref>"Emma Morano compie 115 anni" (in Italian). ogginotizie.it. Retrieved 2014-12-03.</ref>。當別人拜访她時，她說她從不吃藥，一天吃三隻雞蛋并喝一杯自製的白蘭地，有時还會吃巧克力。另外她也會積極面對未來<ref>"Nacque sotto re Umberto I. Era il 1899 Emma Morano è nata a Civiasco 112 anni fa. Oggi vive a Verbania e abita ancora da sola "Martedì ho festeggiato con torta e vino bianco". Mangia tre uova al giorno e beve la "sua" grappa" (in Italian). Civiasco.netweek.it. 1987-07-16. Retrieved 2013-05-05.</ref>。她把自己的長壽歸功於每天吃三隻雞蛋的飲食習慣和單身生活<ref>Bender, Kelli. "Emma Morano, 115, Credits Her Long Life to Raw Eggs and Staying Single". Retrieved 2016-03-12.</ref>。2011年，她作為一項全球研究的一部分跟隨{{link-en|喬治·徹奇|George Church}}到訪[[波士頓|波士頓]]哈佛醫學院，以研究她長壽的秘訣<ref>"Ricercatori Statunitensi E Troupe Rai Da Nonna Emmm" (in Italian). verbaniamilleventi.org. 2007-03-27. Archived from the original on September 27, 2013. Retrieved 2013-05-05.</ref>。同年12月，她獲時任意大利總統[[喬治·納波利塔諾|喬治·納波利塔諾]]頒發{{link-en|意大利共和國榮譽勳章|Order of Merit of the Italian Republic}}<ref>"Le onorificenze della Repubblica italiana" (in Italian). Quirinale.it. Retrieved 2013-05-05.</ref>。2013年4月2日，{{link-en|瑪莉亞·雷特埃利|Maria Redaelli}}（1899–2013）去世，艾瑪·莫拉諾成為意大利最年長的在世人士<ref>mario.giovanardi. "Emma MArano 113 anni Mangio tre uova al giorno, come mi disse il dottore quando ero ragazza" (in Italian). Vip.it. Retrieved 2013-05-05.</ref>。在她114歲生日時，她在[[意大利广播电视公司|RAI]]的節目進行了簡短的電視直播採訪。<ref>"Emma Morano compie 114 anni" (in Italian). ogginotizie.it. Retrieved 2013-11-30.</ref>在她116歲生日時，她收到教宗[[方濟各_(教宗)|方濟各]]的祝賀<ref>"[http://www.ecorisveglio.it/articolo.php?ARTUUID=6899C8F9-3885-4A7B-A5B1-230F992B37BE&MUUID=AFA9393B-B907-4AD0-878F-5C402A0A8219 I 116 anni di Emma Morano] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ecorisveglio.it/articolo.php?ARTUUID=6899C8F9-3885-4A7B-A5B1-230F992B37BE&MUUID=AFA9393B-B907-4AD0-878F-5C402A0A8219 |date=20160304095119 }}". Eco Risveglio. 2015-11-29.</ref>。她分別在2014年8月和2015年8月超越維納斯·皮茲納托（Venere Pizzinato，1896–2011）和[[狄娜·曼佛瑞迪尼|狄娜·曼佛瑞迪尼]]（1897–2012，生於[[義大利|義大利]]，[[移民|移民]]並死於[[美國|美國]]），成為意大利的[[最年長者|最年長者]]<ref>[http://www.diregiovani.it/2016/05/13/34219-nonnina-del-mondo.dg/ Emma Morano, è italiana la nonnina del mondo] {{Wayback|url=http://www.diregiovani.it/2016/05/13/34219-nonnina-del-mondo.dg/ |date=20201021132530 }} Retrieved May 16, 2016.</ref><ref>"[http://www.corrieredinovara.com/it/web/nonna-emma-compie-115-anni-26782/sez/territorio/ Nonna Emma compie 115 anni] {{Wayback|url=http://www.corrieredinovara.com/it/web/nonna-emma-compie-115-anni-26782/sez/territorio/ |date=20171108095633 }}". 29 November 2014. Retrieved 31 January 2016.</ref>。2016年5月13日，[[蘇珊娜·瓊斯|蘇珊娜·瓊斯]]逝世後，她以{{Age in years and days|1899|11|29|2016|5|13}}之齡成為在世的最年長者<ref>"[http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2016/05/13/shes-only-person-left-born-1800s/84321322/ This woman is the only person left born in the 1800s] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2016/05/13/shes-only-person-left-born-1800s/84321322/ |date=20160521214731 }}". USA Today. 13 May 2016.</ref>。2016年7月29日[[吉尼斯世界紀錄|吉尼斯世界紀錄]]正式確認她為在世最年長者，並為她頒發獎章。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.verbaniamilleventi.org/emma-morano-sul-libro-del-guinness-world-records/ |title = Emma Morano Sul Libro Del Guinness World Records |publisher = verbaniamilleventi.org |first = Sergio |last = Ronchi |date = 2 August 2016 |accessdate = 3 August 2016 |language = it |archive-date = 2020-09-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200922063706/https://www.verbaniamilleventi.org/emma-morano-sul-libro-del-guinness-world-records/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.lastampa.it/2016/08/02/edizioni/verbania/cronaca/guinness-e-marianisti-premiano-emma-morano-REkjulAN41rI0pMlwoNhxK/pagina.html |title = Guinness e marianisti premiano Emma Morano |work = La Stampa |first = Sergio |last = Ronchi |date = 2 August 2016 |accessdate = 3 August 2016 |language = it |archive-date = 2018-06-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180629131204/http://www.lastampa.it/2016/08/02/edizioni/verbania/cronaca/guinness-e-marianisti-premiano-emma-morano-REkjulAN41rI0pMlwoNhxK/pagina.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>在她117歲生日的2016年11月29日，她的生日派對過程被當地的電視台直播。<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/29/world/europe/emma-morano-worlds-oldest-person-turns-117.html |title = Emma Morano, World’s Oldest Person, Turns 117 |first = Elisabetta |last = Povoledo |date = 29 November 2016 |work = The New York Times |accessdate = 11 April 2017 |archive-date = 2021-02-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224121612/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/29/world/europe/emma-morano-worlds-oldest-person-turns-117.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>2017年4月15日，莫拉諾在位於[[韋爾巴尼亞|韋爾巴尼亞]]的家中自然死亡，享嵩壽117歲137天<ref>[http://www.vcoazzurratv.it/notizie/prima-pagina/4683-morta-emma-morano-aveva-117-anni-e-137-giorni-4 Morta Emma Morano, aveva 117 anni e 137 giorni] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vcoazzurratv.it/notizie/prima-pagina/4683-morta-emma-morano-aveva-117-anni-e-137-giorni-4 |date=20170416125945 }} {{it icon}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url = http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/italys-emma-morano-worlds-oldest-person-dies-117-46818534 |title = Italy's Emma Morano, the world's oldest person, dies at 117 |last =  |first =  |date = 15 April 2017 |publisher = [[ABC_News|ABC News]] |access-date = 15 April 2017 |language = en |archive-date = 2017-04-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170416044811/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/italys-emma-morano-worlds-oldest-person-dies-117-46818534 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url = http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/nationworld/ct-worlds-oldest-person-dies-20170415-story.html |title = Emma Morano, the world's oldest person, dies in Italy at 117 |last = D'Emilio |first = Frances |date = 15 April 2017 |work = The Chicago Tribune |access-date = 15 April 2017 |language = en-US |archive-date = 2017-04-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170416045108/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/nationworld/ct-worlds-oldest-person-dies-20170415-story.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。在莫拉諾過世時，她是最後一位生於[[1890年代|1890年代]]而在世的人<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.lastampa.it/2017/04/15/edizioni/verbania/verbania-morta-a-anni-emma-morano-era-la-pi-anziana-del-mondo-G5xAoUlH4vWsNB5qAVwXhI/pagina.html |title = Verbania, morta a 117 anni Emma Morano: era la più anziana del mondo |last = Ronchi |first = Sergio |date = 15 April 2017 |website = La Stampa |language = it |accessdate = 15 April 2017 |archive-date = 2017-04-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170420225048/http://www.lastampa.it/2017/04/15/edizioni/verbania/verbania-morta-a-anni-emma-morano-era-la-pi-anziana-del-mondo-G5xAoUlH4vWsNB5qAVwXhI/pagina.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-39610937 |title = World's oldest person Emma Morano dies at 117 |last =  |first =  |date = 15 April 2017 |publisher = BBC News |access-date = 15 April 2017 |language = en-GB |archive-date = 2017-04-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170415184133/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-39610937 |dead-url = no }}</ref>和名列全球有史以來獲驗證最長壽者的第5名，<ref>{{cite news |title = La biografia per la valsesiana più vecchia del mondo |url = http://www.lasesia.vercelli.it/stories/provincia/16858_la_biografia_per_la_valsesiana_pi_vecchia_del_mondo/ |accessdate = 11 January 2017 |publisher = La Sesia |date = 3 January 2017 |language = it |archive-date = 2017-01-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170113030727/http://www.lasesia.vercelli.it/stories/provincia/16858_la_biografia_per_la_valsesiana_pi_vecchia_del_mondo/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url = http://mytoba.ca/featured/worlds-oldest-person-dead-age-117/ |title = World’s Oldest Person Dead At Age 117 |last = Fernando |first = Spencer |date = 15 April 2017 |work = MyToba.ca News |access-date = 8 May 2017 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170416040213/http://mytoba.ca/featured/worlds-oldest-person-dead-age-117/ |archive-date = 2017-04-16 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>如今位列已降為第7名。莫拉諾過世後，[[牙買加|牙買加]]人瑞[[紫羅蘭·布朗|紫羅蘭·布朗]]接任在世最年長者。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/italys-emma-morano-the-worlds-oldest-person-dies-at-117/2017/04/15/7e75462e-2200-11e7-bb59-a74ccaf1d02f_story.html |title = Italy's Emma Morano, the world's oldest person, dies at 117 |last = D'Emilio |first = Frances |date = 15 April 2017 |website = The Washington Post |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170415230128/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/italys-emma-morano-the-worlds-oldest-person-dies-at-117/2017/04/15/7e75462e-2200-11e7-bb59-a74ccaf1d02f_story.html|archive-date =2017-04-15|dead-url =yes|access-date = 15 April 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url = https://www.statnews.com/2017/04/15/italys-emma-morano-the-worlds-oldest-person-dies-at-117/ |title = Italy’s Emma Morano, the world’s oldest person, dies at 117 |last =  |first =  |date = 15 April 2017 |publisher = STAT News |access-date = 15 April 2017 |via = Associated Press |archive-date = 2017-04-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170416220734/https://www.statnews.com/2017/04/15/italys-emma-morano-the-worlds-oldest-person-dies-at-117/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

